org.eclipse.smarthome.core.library.unit

Class MetricPrefix

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.smarthome.core.library.unit.MetricPrefix

  • @NonNullByDefault
public class MetricPrefix
extends Object
    The metric prefixes used to derive units by specific powers of 10. This delegates to the enum instances of MetricPrefix.
